quote_first: From twenty minutes past nine until twenty-seven minutes past nine, from twenty-five minutes past eleven until
quote_last: , from ten minutes to three until two minutes to three the heroes of the school met in a large familiarity whose Olympian laughter awed the fearful small boy that flitted uneasily past and chilled the slouching senior that rashly paused to examine the notices in assertion of an unearned right.
title: Sinister Street
author: Compton Mackenzie
